form.text: Masks, is it okay to take them off indoors?
Can I take my mask off in all instances at indoors?

Indoor masks are not required, only in public transport,pharmacies
and hospitals. In case of a cold, wear a mask at all times.
What can I do if I have certain symptoms?
If you have symptoms of a cold or came in contact with an infected person, please wear a mask regardless your settings.
The difference between mandatory and voluntary use

You can be charged if failing to wear a mask when mandatory.
At any other case, it is recommended but free to decide.
What in case of public gyms and pools?

The use of mask is not mandatory at these
public places but is up to the user’s will.
